column1: I am incredibly grateful to be endorsed by Vice President @JoeBiden. I look forward to working with Joe and @KamalaHarris next year as we get through this COVID crisis and build back better than before. #FL07 #FlaPol https://t.co/72cXj7Nbx0

THIS JUST IN --> Today we released our first television ad of the campaign calling for less partisanship and more patriotism to get us through this COVID crisis. Check it out here -- and then share to help us get the word out! #FL07 #FlaPol #TeamMurphy https://t.co/CfNhgUUXHX

With the US death toll from COVID surpassing 173000 Trump has failed our country. Tonight @MikeBloomberg reinforced the message of this critical moment the call for true leadership and why @JoeBiden and @KamalaHarris will get us through this. #DemConvention #FlaPol

I agree with @nikkifried! Please support @HattersleyforFL. He'll join me in Congress in supporting women tackling climate change and helping families through this COVID crisis. He is the strongest Dem to win in November! PLEASE VOTE! #FlaPol #FL15 https://t.co/nGD43pTFKI

My Op-Ed on CNN on how Congress is facing the ultimate test of leadership during this #COVID19 crisis. We must work better together in order to get “swift simple and sufficient” aid to the American people. #FL07 #FlaPol  https://t.co/H9lyCx2jnW
THIS JUST IN from @FL_Daily: "Stephanie Murphy: HHS Sending Almost $2 Million to True Health Clinics in Central Florida to Help With Coronavirus" https://t.co/VuYGZ89DU0 #FL07 #FlaPol #COVID19
From @FL_Daily: "Despite Self Quarantine Stephanie Murphy Continues to Focus on Coronavirus" READ MORE: https://t.co/Gf3GgMwV5Q #FL07 #FlaPol #COVID19US

Proud to stand with my @HouseBlueDogs colleagues in demanding that Congress produce a balanced economic rescue package that focuses on the middle class. Both parties must balance lessons of the past with the realities we face today. https://t.co/TJft00aV4d #FL07 #FlaPol #COVID19

“Due to the rapidly accelerating spread of coronavirus it is essential that Florida’s governor use his power to immediately close access to all public beaches in the state of Florida...if we want to successfully slow the spread of the virus.” #FL07 #FlaPol #COVID19 https://t.co/vRhrEgmVSR

While there are very legitimate criticisms of how China has handled coronavirus @POTUS using this xenophobic term to label #COVID19 is unproductive & invites unfair discrimination & harassment toward Asian Americans. We’re all in this together & we must unite to stop the spread. https://t.co/vlmM8lvPaY
If you are a Florida voter and have concerns about voting due to #COVID19 I strongly encourage you to vote by mail or vote early. Get more info at https://t.co/dkPzl6B6gJ. #FlaPol
